    ('Beta Channel Update','Monday, March 9, 2015','The Chrome engineering team is excited to announce the promotion of Chrome 42 to the beta channel for Windows, Mac and Linux. Chrome 42.0.2311.22 contains many improvements including:A number of new apps/extension APIs (including the Push API!)Lots of under the hood changes for stability and performanceThe answer to life, the universe, and everythingA full list of changes in this build is available in the log. Find out more at the Chrome and Chromium blogs. Interested in switching release channels? Find out how. If you find a new issue, please let us know by filing a bug.Alex MineerGoogle Chrome'),
