    ('Chrome for Android Update','Thursday, November 1, 2012','The stable channel of Chrome for Android has been updated to 18.0.1025464 for ARM devices and to 18.0.1026320 for x86 devices. The new update includes important stability fixes and support for the Nexus 4 and Nexus 10. Both updates are now available for download on Google Play and in the Google Play Store on your mobile devices. Known issues are available on the Chrome support site.If you find a new issue, please let us know by filing a bug. More information on Chrome for Android is available on the Chrome site.Vinod RamachandranGoogle Chrome'),
