    ('Chrome for Android Beta Update','Wednesday, June 6, 2012','Chrome for Android Beta has been updated to 0.18.4531.3636 on Google Play. In addition to changes through Chrome 18.0.1025.166 and a minor reorganization of Settings options, this update focuses primarily on stability and performance improvements.Known issues:113041 : No way to auto-hide the toolbar114964 : Error pages are not optimized for mobile / Android devicesOther notable issues listed hereIf you find a new issue, please let us know by filing a bug. More information about Chrome for Android is available on the Chrome site.Srikanth RajagopalanGoogle Chrome'),
