    ('Beta Channel Update','Friday, March 16, 2012','The Beta channel has been updated to 18.0.1025.108 for Windows, Mac, Linux, and Chrome Frame.This release changes to V8 version 3.7 and it contains fixes for a number of stability issues along with other bugs. Full details about what changes are in this build are available in the SVN revision log. Interested in switching to the Beta channel? Find out how. If you find a new issue, please let us know by filing a bug.Karen GrunbergGoogle Chrome'),
